# Cloudflare Pages redirects
# Doc: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/

# Locale fallback: bare /tools redirects to default locale (next-intl middleware also handles this on dev,
# but a static redirect is faster at the edge for tools deep-linked without a locale prefix).
/tools                  /en/tools                  302
/tools/*                /en/tools/:splat           302
/about                  /en/about                  302
/privacy                /en/privacy                302
/terms                  /en/terms                  302
/contact                /en/contact                302
